In my trouble and distress,
He answered, He delivered.
Thank the Lord for His goodness!

When I was lost,
I asked for directions,
You guided me by Your hand.

I cried in my emptiness,
The Lord turned His ear and heard.
In my trouble and distress,
He answered, He delivered.
Thank the Lord for His goodness!

